name: Fish Feeding
description:
My Mom asks me to draw fish because it's good luck.
My mom ask me to draw a fish so she could post it on the wall of our house because she believe owning a fish or having a symbol of a fish gives good luck to the people near it. The art shows that the boy is showing his lunch to the group of fish and the group of fish is somehow attracted to that food. let be this art piece attract all the good lucks in 2022 :)
